Definition: having a red face from embarrassment or shame or agitation or emotional upset
Example: the blushing boy was brought before the Principal; her blushful beau; was red-faced with anger
Synonyms: blushing, a, red-faced, having, red, face, from, embarrassment, or, shame, agitation, emotional, upset, the, boy, was, brought, before, Principal, her, beau, with, anger
Category: adj.all
